  "text": "Conjecture 2 (Martin [CITATION_1] ) Fix p 0 ∈ (0, 1) and let H = Forb(G(n 0 , p 0 )). Then ed H (p) = (1 + o(1)) 2 log 2 n 0 n 0 min p − log 2 (1 − p 0 ) , 1 − p − log 2 p 0 with probability approaching 1 as n 0 → ∞.",
